description: The Pakistan cricket team became a full member of the International cricket council in the year 1952 following a recommendation from India. Several Pakistan players have played under the India cricket team before the separation. Currently, the ICC rankings are Test 7th, ODI 6th, and t20I 1st.
name: Pakistan cricket team
